{
  "chapter": 131,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述寇仲、徐子陵、跋锋寒三人藏身李密船队，偷听李密与郑石如、钱独关等人的军事会议。李密志在东都洛阳，计划分兵牵制王世充，再以精兵逼东都。白清儿暗中通知阴癸派追杀李密。三人趁机偷取快艇北上洛阳，途中跋锋寒评价长白双凶符真、符彦的追踪本领，并讲述董淑妮、石青璇等人物。跋锋寒谈及对男女之情的看法，认为生命在于不断挑战新鲜。寇仲急于北上洛阳，声称要做一笔情报买卖，实则身怀杨公宝库秘密。三人谈笑间，前方河道出现灯火，预示新变故。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阴癸派妖女最懂收藏，但我精于观人之道，所以她休想瞒得过我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "发为血之馀，只要你留意她头发的色泽，便知她的体魄绝不像她外形般柔弱，而且有精湛的气功底子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她皮肤的娇嫩亦非天生的，而是长期修练某种魔功的现象，白得来隐泛亮光，就像婠婠那样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄还有看出甚么来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_li_mi",
      "text": "徐军师之议容后再论，在下尚有一事想请教密公。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "郑先生请直言无碍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_li_mi",
      "text": "宇文化及杀死那昏君后，率兵北归，志在洛阳。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_li_mi",
      "text": "以密公之才智，为何不诈作与宇文化及联同一线，任宇文化及攻打东都，再坐收渔人之利？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_li_mi",
      "text": "现在却是反其道而行，平白帮了王世充一个天大的忙，更使他得以保存实力，观之目下王世充挥军东下，兵至偃师便知他是要趁密公损折了大量兵员后，想趁机占点便宜！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_li_mi",
      "text": "密公有否为此心生悔意呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "郑先生不愧河南智者，对局势了若指掌。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "不过李密亦有一个问题欲请教先生，假若设身置地，换了先生处在李密的位置，面对宇文化及南来的十万精兵，会如何应付？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "如果一旦洛阳被宇文化及所破，使其既有坚城为据点，又粮食充足，宇文化及的大军便再非远道而来的疲惫之师，我李密再与之争锋，那是否划算的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_li_mi",
      "text": "密公之言有理，不过目下形势显然不利密公，密公有何对策。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王世充只是我手下败将，何足言勇。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现今他率众而来，洛阳必虚，我李密只要分兵守其东来之路，令他难作寸进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另外再以精兵数万，傍河西以逼东都，那时世充必还，我们则退守南方，按兵不动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mi",
      "speaker_name": "李密",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如世充再出，我又逼之，如此我绰有馀力，彼则徒劳往返，破之必矣。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "徐世绩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王世充移师东来攻我，粮食不足，志在速战，只要我们深沟高垒以拒之，只须两三个月光景，王世充粮绝必退，那时我们再衔尾追击，王世充能有命回洛阳，便是他家山有福。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_qian_du_guan",
      "text": "只听密公和徐军师这番话，便知瓦岗军胜券在握，王世充有难矣。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_qian_du_guan",
      "text": "城主还要犹豫吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "李密今趟有难了，刚才她定是以秘密手法通知本派的人，好调动人手，追杀李密，现在她则是准备追踪李密，掌握他的去向。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "李密是这么容易被狙杀死的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若祝玉妍亲来又如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "白清儿这么去了，不怕钱独关回来寻她不着吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "她自然比我们更清楚钱独关的行事作风。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "嘿！我有个提议；不如把那两大叠书画纸放到白妖女的闺房内，然后再追上李密，看看可否沾点油水。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "悉随尊便！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不若躲到其中一条小艇去，除非他们要用艇，否则该是最安全的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若那长白双傻留下来找我们，便真是笑话之极！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你知道他们是甚么人吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "听跋兄这么说，这两个家伙该是有点道行的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人是王薄的师弟，不过早与师兄反目，想不到现在投靠了李密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人虽赋性骄横狂妄，但确有点真本领，否则早给王薄宰掉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尤其长兄符真更是有名擅长追踪的高手，这方面比李密以前死去的手下飞羽郑踪更有名气，武功更是天壤云泥之别，幸好我们躲到这里来，否则会有天大的烦恼呢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "趁此机会，我们先养好精神，待会杀人时，也爽快一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不是要泊岸吧！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岸上有人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来李密伏兵在此，若与钱独关谈判失败，便以奇兵攻襄阳之不备，确是狠辣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "谁都知李密非是善男信女，徐兄这猜测颇合李密作风。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了，现在给个天祝玉妍做胆，恐怕她也不敢来惹李密，我们该怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们立即偷艘快艇，北上洛阳。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若现在去偷艇，就不是暗偷而是明抢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李密本身高明不在话下，他手下亦不乏高手，我们未必能成功的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "为何仲少这么急于到洛阳去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "迟些再向你们解释，暗偷不成就明抢吧！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看！李密上岸了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就是李密麾下大将裴仁基，此人与王伯当齐名，人称瓦岗双虎将，武功高强，智计过人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要抢船，现在正是时候！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_anonymous",
      "speaker_name": "岸上有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们三个在干甚么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "烦请告诉密公，跋锋寒、寇仲、徐子陵借船去也。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟我们是明着剃李密的眼眉，迫他派人来追杀我们，淆水北端尽于洛阳南面三百里处，那段路途会最是精采。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "凭我们现在快若奔马的行舟速度，李密的人如何能追上我们。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若李密只是一般贼寇，当然奈何不了我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但瓦岗军现在已成了一个严密组织的军事集团，更因要占夺东都，故在这一带设置了能火速传递军事情报的网络，一旦有事，便可利用快马驿站，又或飞鸽传讯的方式，指示远方的手下进行任何行动，所以我们切不能松懈下来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今次北上洛阳，我们只宜智胜，不宜硬闯，只要我们能以最快速度赶抵洛阳，便算我们赢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "长白双傻给撇下在襄阳，李密和裴仁基、徐世绩又难以分身，会否是俏军师沈落雁来侍候我们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最好前来的是王伯当，我们便可向他讨回旧债了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "少有见徐兄对一个人如此恨之入骨的，不过王伯当一手双尖软矛使得非常出色，名列奇功绝艺榜上，就算他落了单，要杀他亦非易事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们听过董淑妮的芳名吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "从未听过，不过这名字倒很别致。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "董淑妮是王世充妹子王馨的独生女，自幼父母双亡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此女年华十八，生得花容月貌，国色天香，艳盖洛阳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄是否有意追逐裙下呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对我来说，男女之情只是镜花水月，刹那芳华，既不能持久，更没有永恒的价值。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "况且此女实王世充最大的政治本钱，听说李阀亦对此女有意，希望凭此与王世充结成联盟，对抗李密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若她嫁与李世民，确是郎才女貌，非常匹配。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄只想当然罢了！因为听说要纳董淑妮的是李渊本人！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "当年我们曾在东平郡听石青璇吹箫，石青璇走时跋兄曾追她去了，结果如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只能看到她的背影，但已留下了永不磨灭的深刻印象。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这在彼此来说都或者是最好的情况，若我和她朝夕相对，说不定终有一天生出厌倦之心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄是否很矛盾呢？一方面说不介怀男女之情，另一方面却对有色艺的美女渴望追寻，又铭记于心。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "难怪徐兄有此误会，皆因常见我与不同的美女混在一起，现在又听我说不把男女之情放在心上。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "但事实上这两者并无必然对立的情况。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄于此尚有何高论？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自懂人事以来，我便感到生命是不断的重复，每天都大致上干着同一样的事，只有不断的改变环境，不断地应付新的挑战，或把自己不断陷进不同的境况内，才可感受到生命新鲜动人的一面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像现在般就没有半丝重覆或沉闷的感觉，摆在眼前正是个茫不可测的未来，似乎在你掌握中，又若全不受你控制。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和两位的合作更是刺激有趣，谁能肯定下一刻我们不会遇上祝玉妍呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是我不想把男女之情放在心上的原因之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这么说，跋兄可是个天生薄情的负心汉了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你莫要笑我，我和你都是有野心的人，只不过我专志武道，而你则作你的霸业皇帝梦；道路虽然不同，但若要达成目标，都须作出种种舍弃。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "我何时告诉你本人要作皇帝梦？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "观其行知其志，你寇仲把南方搞得天翻地覆，形势大变，又身怀杨公宝库的秘密北上，已为你的计划作了最好的说明。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "昨晚在藏青阁的画室内分明听到了至关重要的机密，但偏要藏在心内，否则为何这么急于到洛阳去呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老跋你果有一手，想瞒你真是难以登天。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过我今次上洛阳，只是想做一笔买卖，别人出钱，我卖情报，与甚么作皇帝梦没有任何关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐兄相信吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "我不想骗跋兄，又不想开罪仲少，只好避而不答。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 131,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 343
    }
